Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.51,0:37:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好\NOkay, Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.15,0:39:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,（法语）大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.26,0:39:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,（缅甸语）你们好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.67,0:39:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（希伯来语）你好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.78,0:39:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）你好 向大家致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.29,0:39:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）女士们先生们 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.85,0:39:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）再见期待下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.78,0:39:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）用克丘亚语向你们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.89,0:39:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）每一个人问好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.67,0:39:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,（旁遮普语）欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.61,0:39:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,（赫梯语）你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.65,0:39:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（孟加拉语）你好 愿到处都有和平
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.49,0:39:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）无论你们是谁 你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.08,0:39:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）我们对你们心怀善意
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.06,0:39:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）并带着和平穿梭星际
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.80,0:39:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[左声道 右声道]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.73,0:39:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚兰语）你好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.30,0:39:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,（荷兰语）向每个人致以诚挚的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.57,0:39:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,（德语）向所有人致以诚挚的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.65,0:39:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）愿和平与你们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.79,0:39:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）我们代表地球的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.76,0:39:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（基洛纳区-监视点J3 1990年6月29日）]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.70,0:39:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.58,0:40:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉来晚了\NSorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.25,0:40:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,路上堵死了 我又没法早点走\NTraffic was hell, and I couldn't leave early.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.05,0:40:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 趁还有时间聊聊吧\NLet's just use the time we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.22,0:40:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今天感觉怎么样 克拉克？\NHow are you today, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.42,0:40:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看得我怎么样？\NHow do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.69,0:40:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的 可能有点累吧\NFine. A little tired, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.36,0:40:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直糟糕透了\NI look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.43,0:40:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想确认一下\NCan I ask, and there is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.80,0:40:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放心回答 没什么对错\Nno wrong answer here, you know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.77,0:40:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是不是受到酒精影响？\NAre you intoxicated right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.47,0:40:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛这么问？\NWhy you say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.94,0:40:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么问了？\NLike what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.84,0:40:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我从周五起就没碰过一滴酒\NI haven't had a drink since Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.71,0:40:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没准儿我这副鬼样子就是因为没喝酒\NIt's probably why I look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.05,0:40:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能问你个事吗？ - 请说\N- Can I ask you something? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.28,0:40:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你把人强制关精神病院过吗？\NYou ever 5150'd someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.28,0:40:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[【加州法律5150条：强制将危险精神病人送院观察】]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.45,0:40:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年确实有过几次 只要情况需要\NA few times over the years, when it was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.66,0:40:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那...那...那什么样的情况才算需要？\NWh-wha-what makes it necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.16,0:40:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我认为对方有伤人自残的风险\NIf I believe that the person is a danger to themselves or others,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.49,0:41:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,或者无法自理\Nor they're gravely disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.37,0:41:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,行 行 \NOkay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.54,0:41:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.94,0:41:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我在店里发现了点情况\NI found something in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.44,0:41:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好 什么情况\NOkay. What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.05,0:41:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.72,0:41:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是个地方 我...\NA place. I f...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.42,0:41:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现了个地方\NI found a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.09,0:41:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,地方？\NA place?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.39,0:41:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉...\NYeah. It's like, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.93,0:41:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉店就那样...\NIt's like the store just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.66,0:41:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,往外扩了\Ncontinues, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.00,0:41:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧...店有墙\NIt's like... you know, like there's a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.90,0:41:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,墙后头居然还是店\Nand on the other side of the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.23,0:41:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了地往外扩\Nthe store just keeps going, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.04,0:41:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 就像 像个克隆的 \Nlike-like a... like a copy of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.34,0:41:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我猜入口是用镜子什么的给挡住的\NI-I-I figure they're using mirrors or something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.11,0:41:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\Nto hide the entrance, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.01,0:41:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我没听明白\NSorry, I'm not following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.84,0:41:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说找到了个之前没发现的房间？\NIs this a room you didn't know about before?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.98,0:41:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.68,0:41:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是...就是你一进去后\NOkay, so y-y-you go in and, uh, at first
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.71,0:41:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看着像个...像个写字楼\Nit just looks like a- like an office building.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.75,0:41:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一个巨大的办公室 你懂吧？\NLike a... like a huge office building, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.72,0:41:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...你 你继续往里走\NAnd then, uh... But then you-you keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.76,0:41:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,接着...接着你就发现\Nand then-then you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.89,0:42:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所...所有东西都不对劲\Nth-th-that none of it makes any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.36,0:42:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢...嗯...想象一下\NIt's-it's like, um... Imagine describing a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.93,0:42:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你给个没见过狗的人描述狗\Nto someone who's never seen one before
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.13,0:42:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让那人把狗画出来\Nand then asking them to draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.80,0:42:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会画对几个地方\NThey might get some things right, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.80,0:42:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝不可能全画对\Nbut there's no way they'd get everything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.57,0:42:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 诡异的在于细节\NYou know, the devil's in the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.84,0:42:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以远看像只狗\NSo from a distance, you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.51,0:42:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但凑近一看...\Nyou think you're seeing a dog, but then you look clos--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.94,0:42:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛那样看我？\NWhy are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.78,0:42:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在试着理解\NI'm just trying to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.21,0:42:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呵\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.05,0:42:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不像个心理医生 怎么表情都写在脸上\NYou know, for a shrink, you got a terrible poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.59,0:42:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的这些听起来很离奇\NWhat you're saying might sound fantastical,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.72,0:42:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但并不危险\Nbut not dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.59,0:42:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那些办公室里有人吗？\NAre there any people in these offices?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.63,0:42:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没见过 但我能听到\NNot that I've seen. You know, I hear, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.90,0:42:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,听到脚步声 而且...而且我一转眼\NThere's footsteps, an-an-and stuff gets moved around
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.74,0:42:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,东西就被挪了位置\Nwhen I'm not looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.84,0:42:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这听起来很离谱 但你得明白\NI know how this sounds, but you've got to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.31,0:42:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方太大了\Nit's massive in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.94,0:42:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,简直像纽约地铁那么大 懂吧\NLike New-York's-subway-system massive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.14,0:42:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没准儿里面有好几百人\NFor all I know, there's hundreds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.68,0:42:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是没看到\NI just haven't seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.15,0:43:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.52,0:43:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 这就像个...\NYou see? It's like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.12,0:43:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就像个迷宫\NIt's like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.26,0:43:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没尽头\NIt just goes on and on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.59,0:43:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时候真怕自己会迷路\NSometimes I'm scared I'll get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.53,0:43:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么除了你 没人发现这地方？\NWhy do you think no one else has found this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.50,0:43:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.87,0:43:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但入口在负一层\NThe entrance is on the subfloor,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.97,0:43:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以整个结构\Nso the whole structure is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.97,0:43:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,估计都在地下 懂吧\Nprobably underground, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.01,0:43:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,地图上根本没这个地方\NIt's not on any city maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.87,0:43:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,入口根本看不出来 谁会想到去找？\NThe entrances are hidden, so who'd think to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.71,0:43:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说不信你...\NI'm not saying I don't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.81,0:43:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 你跟我说\Nbut you told me yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.68,0:43:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你周五就开始戒酒了\Nyou haven't had a drink since Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.55,0:43:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这会不会导致幻.... - 行了\N- Do you think there is a-- - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.29,0:43:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 停 停\N- Clark-- - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.96,0:43:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果这是真的... - 行 我懂了 多谢您啊\N- If this is true-- - Yeah, I get it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.46,0:43:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟早会带着证据回来\NYou know, I'm gonna come back here with proof
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.03,0:43:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候你得给我好好道歉\Nand you're gonna owe me a serious fucking apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.58,0:44:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯\NKat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.92,0:44:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁呀 来了 来了\NJesus, goddamn, I'm coming! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.53,0:44:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 克船长？\N- Hey. - Cap'n Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.43,0:44:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 额... - 等等 等等 小凯 快来\N- Um... - Wait, wait, wait, wait. Kat?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.53,0:44:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我来了 - 快点\N- I'm coming. - Kat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.90,0:44:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 我来了\NOkay, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.33,0:44:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是这样的... - 搞什么鬼\N- Look-- -What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.00,0:44:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那个...\NYeah, I'm sorry, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.60,0:44:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们明天有空吗？\NWhat are you guys doing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.24,0:45:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.00,0:45:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我给钱 算加班 顶多两个小时 很快的\NI'll pay you. Two hours. Overtime. Tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.94,0:45:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,行 给钱干什么？\NOkay, pay us for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.78,0:45:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,做调研\NResearch.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.75,0:45:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,摄像机还在你们那儿吧？\NYou got the camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.08,0:45:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能...能再帮我拍点东西吗？\NYou can-you can borrow it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.69,0:45:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,行不行？\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.96,0:45:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 开始拍了\NOkay, we are rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.66,0:45:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿摆了些东西\NWe got, um, some shit over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.92,0:45:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[车停]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.73,0:45:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还有停车牌\NWe got some stop signs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.60,0:45:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 呃 绳子\Nand, uh... a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.04,0:45:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拿绳子干嘛？\NWhat's the rope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.30,0:45:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,装备\NSupplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.84,0:45:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 看来咱们要被他绑了\NOh, great, he's gonna tie us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.98,0:45:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我绑 是要给自己绑好\NNo, we're gonna tie ourselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.04,0:45:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 挺重口味的\NHmm. Kinky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.45,0:45:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.85,0:45:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 你还没说清楚\NUh, you still haven't told us
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.01,0:45:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这儿干嘛？\Nwhat we're doing here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.05,0:45:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 做调研\NI did tell you. Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.32,0:45:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是调研装备\NThese are supplies, and we're using them for research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.19,0:45:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么难理解吧\NIt's not that hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.62,0:45:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,行 研究什么？\NOkay, research for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.73,0:45:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你得具体点 老哥\NY-you gotta be more specific, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.06,0:45:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进门了\NI'm gonna go through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.40,0:46:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么门？\NWhat door?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.93,0:46:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是门\NThat's the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.10,0:46:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我在另一边也贴了框\NI taped an outline on the other side, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.94,0:46:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,以防咱们找不到\Njust to help us find our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.37,0:46:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿博？ - 怎么了？\N- Bobby? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.74,0:46:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这很离谱 但得听我的\NLook, I know it sounds crazy, but follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.05,0:46:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.75,0:46:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在天亮前赶回来\NI want to be back before sunup.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.68,0:46:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 现在才晚上九点 你说什么...\NDude, it's like 9 p.m. What the fuck are you talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.12,0:46:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么情况 克拉克 - 卧槽\N- What the fuck! Clark?! - What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.39,0:46:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么做到的？ - 老哥 你...\N- How did you do that? - Dude, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.16,0:46:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到了吧？他怎么会...呃...\NDid you fucking see that?! H-how did he, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.63,0:46:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿 快进来看看\NI'm right here. Come see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.29,0:46:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼 你居然真的...\NWhat the fuck? D-did you just fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.06,0:46:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？怎么会...\NWhat? How the f...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.13,0:46:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢？阿博 快住手\NBobby, stop. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.77,0:46:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去 - 克拉克 你在哪儿？\N- What the fuck?! - Clark, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.27,0:46:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 你...你看到了没？\NHa! Hey, did you... did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.14,0:46:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他钻哪去了？ - 看到了 阿博 我看到了\N- Where the fuck did he go? - Yes, Bobby, I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.37,0:46:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 搞什...\NOh! Where the f--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.17,0:46:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,踏进来就行 没事的\NJust step through the door, you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.14,0:46:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,疯了吧 你得先解释清楚\NWhat?! No! Tell us what is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.15,0:46:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢 直接...\NYou know what, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.65,0:46:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 阿博 别进去 阿博 快停下 你要干什么？\NNo, Bobby, wait! Bobby! Wait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.35,0:46:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.08,0:46:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我去啊\NWhat the fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.55,0:46:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥\NDude!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.95,0:46:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 这怎么可能？\NDude, how is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.76,0:47:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿博 克拉克 - 行...\N- Bobby! Clark! - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.03,0:47:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在哪？里面到底是什么地方？\NWhere are you? What the fuck is back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.63,0:47:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事 小凯 没事的\NNo, no, no, Kat, it's good, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.00,0:47:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧进来看看\NJ-just, you gotta come see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.23,0:47:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...对 你看...\NI mean... Right, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.24,0:47:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这 呃...\NYou see, it's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.91,0:47:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没问题 - 克拉克 这是什么地方？\N- It's fine. - Clark, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.17,0:47:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们在哪？ - 哦\N- Where are we? - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.97,0:47:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也正想弄明白呢\NThat's what I'm trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.08,0:47:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这...这是谁的东西？\NWhose, um... Whose shit is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.15,0:47:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是你...是你店里的吗？\NIs it-is it... is it part of your store?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.01,0:47:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真有主的话\NIf it belongs to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.55,0:47:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还没碰到那个人 - 好吧\N- I haven't met them yet. - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.32,0:47:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,自从发现这地方 我每晚都来\NI've been in here every night since I found the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.19,0:47:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但也就看了个冰山一角\Nand I still barely scratched the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.09,0:47:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,走 我带你们看看\NCome on. I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.46,0:47:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,越往后越有意思\NIt only gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.16,0:47:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真扯... - 嘿 嘿\N- What the fuck... - Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.46,0:47:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得他给我们下药了吧？\NYou don't think he, like, dosed us or something, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.23,0:47:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？没那回事 咱们没磕药\NWhat? No, no, no. We're not on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.30,0:47:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我嗨了 肯定能感觉到\NI think I'd be able to tell if I was high.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.40,0:47:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就嗨着呢\NYou are high!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.50,0:47:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抽草不算\NPot doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.84,0:47:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...这就像...\NSo, um, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.88,0:47:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,像个空办公区？\Nwhat, like an empty office building?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.68,0:47:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿？算是吧 但这地方简直像是\NIn here? Sure. But it's like it was made
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.11,0:47:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一帮嗑嗨了的建筑工盖出来的\Nby a bunch of construction workers on acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.05,0:48:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还搞了个泳池\NThere's even a pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.65,0:48:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有泳池？\NThere's a pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.12,0:48:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 算是吧\NYeah. I mean, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.02,0:48:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟上\NKeep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.36,0:48:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,“车停”什么鬼？\N"Pots." What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.53,0:48:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 那是我上次走的路\NYeah, no, no, that's the way I went last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.47,0:48:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我想找个楼梯下去什么的\NYeah, when I was looking for a staircase down or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.57,0:48:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,结果只发现了个...\NOnly thing I found so far is basically more of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.44,0:48:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的...\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.28,0:48:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 其实就是个斜坡\NI don't know, it's like a ramp, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.68,0:48:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这儿 呃...前面\NIt's, uh... It's up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.92,0:48:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到了\NWe'll be at it in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.05,0:48:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.99,0:48:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这下面总共有多少层？\NHow many floors does it go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.29,0:48:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能用楼层来...\NIs this not technically...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.86,0:48:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 开始拍了吗？\NOkay. All right, you filming?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.60,0:48:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拍了  - 行\N- Yeah. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.26,0:48:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非得让阿博下去？\NI don't see why Bobby has to be the one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.13,0:48:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想去 - 摄像机在他手上\N- I want to. - He's the one with the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.70,0:48:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,相机又没长在他身上\NWell, it's not like it's attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.07,0:48:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它挂在我学生证上的\NYeah, well, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.64,0:48:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就算长在身上了\Nto my student ID, yeah, it kinda is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.57,0:48:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要是觉得不对劲 就拽一下 我把你拉上来 明白吧？\NAny trouble, just give a tug, and I'll pull you up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.41,0:48:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不对劲？克拉克 下面有什么不对劲？\NTrouble? Clark, what fucking trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.94,0:48:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的\NThere's not going to be any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.21,0:49:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 宝贝 没事\NBabe, babe, babe, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.55,0:49:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别下... - 真的没事 我没问题\N- No, hey-- - It's good. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.01,0:49:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你不用下去\NBaby, you don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.71,0:49:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我就是想看看下面有什么\NNo, it's cool. I-I just want to see what's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.42,0:49:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不好奇吗？ - 简直是疯了\N- Are you not curious? - This is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.72,0:49:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能走多远就走多远 - 没事 你看 你看\N- Just go as far as you can. - No, look, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.45,0:49:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不用绳子也能走下去\NYou can basically walk down without a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.12,0:49:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 一点也不陡\NIt's fine, and it's not even steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.36,0:49:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.12,0:49:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好 但有一件事\NOkay, just don't... just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.83,0:49:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,万一我回不来 记得告诉我妈我爱她哦\NIf I don't come back, you'll tell my mom I love her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.13,0:49:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行 - 那么 走吧\N- Okay. - All right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.70,0:49:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好 慢慢来\NAll right, just take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.30,0:49:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.97,0:49:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 实际上还挺陡的\NOh, it is actually kind of steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.37,0:49:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事吧？ - 没事\N- You good? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.11,0:49:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拉紧点 别把我摔了 - 放心\N- Just, uh... try not to drop me. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.05,0:49:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,需要放绳子告诉我\NTell me how much you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.35,0:49:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喔...慢点\NWhoa... Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.29,0:49:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么...喔 喔 喔 操 啊\NWhat the... Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! Fuck! Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.66,0:49:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你上面怎么拉的绳子？\NWhat the fuck are you guys doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.26,0:49:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起\NSorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.07,0:49:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,绳子卡在床腿上了\NIt was stuck around the leg of the bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.67,0:49:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？ - 行 没事\N- Are you okay? - Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.97,0:50:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是绝了\NJesus fucking Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.30,0:50:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,继续放绳子\NJust keep letting me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.14,0:50:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 来了\NAll right. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.96,0:50:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我下来了\NOkay, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.80,0:50:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看到什么没？\NSee anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.13,0:50:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUgh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.20,0:50:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 就是...\NUh, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.67,0:50:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一堆脏衣服和垃圾\NIt's a bunch of laundry and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.51,0:50:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？衣服？\NWhat do you mean? Clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.58,0:50:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对 这下面真是臭死了\NYeah, it just fucking stinks down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.11,0:50:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么吗？\NSee anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.48,0:50:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有 呃...给我点时间\NYeah, just, uh... Just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.21,0:50:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.85,0:50:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\NOh, god...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.66,0:50:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[结束南非种族隔离]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.60,0:51:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.00,0:51:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[【结束南非种族隔离：是80年代盛行的现实世界口号】]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.04,0:51:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博？\NBobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.54,0:51:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.37,0:51:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就想确认下你没事\NJust checking that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.14,0:51:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我没事 只是 呃...\NYeah, I'm fine. Just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.95,0:51:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.08,0:51:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.02,0:51:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.33,0:51:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\NWhat the fuck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.94,0:51:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博？快上来\NBobby? Come back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.34,0:51:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里发毛\NI don't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.21,0:51:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 呃...再多放点绳子\NHey! Uh... Let some more line out!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.64,0:51:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 已经到头了\NI can't! It's as far as it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.68,0:51:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\NFuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.02,0:52:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我操 快拉我上去\NFuck! Pull me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.22,0:52:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 怎么了？\NBobby! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.76,0:52:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 操 - 你看到了什么？\N- Fuck! - What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.59,0:52:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,磨蹭什么 快把他拉上来\NWhat the fuck is it? Pull him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.93,0:52:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在拉啊 我的天 - 操\N- I am! Jesus Christ! -Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.13,0:52:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拉快点\NPull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.43,0:52:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快拉 老哥 搞什么鬼\NPull, man! What the fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.77,0:52:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,绳子绕到我脚上了\NIt's getting caught on my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.43,0:52:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绳子绕到我脚上了 - 快点使劲拉\N- I can't pull-- - Fucking pull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.24,0:52:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 快点拉\NClark, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.74,0:52:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了 快到了 宝贝 坚持住\NAlmost here! Almost here, babe, just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.68,0:52:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快把他拉上来 - 你看到了什么？\N- Pull him up! - What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.84,0:52:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,下...下面有人\NThere's, uh, there's someone down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.75,0:52:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你安全了...什么？- 操\N- We've got you. What? - Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.28,0:52:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点说 深呼吸 宝贝 没事了\NSlow down, just breathe. Baby, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.92,0:52:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快把这破玩意儿给我解开 操 真是够了\NJust get this shit off me, man. Fuck. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.68,0:52:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事了 没事了 - 你看到了什么？\N-I t's okay. It's okay. - What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.99,0:52:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 深呼吸 - 这打的什么破结？\N- Here. Hey, deep breath. - What kind of knot is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.15,0:52:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸...\NDeep breath--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.49,0:52:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卧槽？！ - 哎 哎 哎\N- What the fuck?! - Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.02,0:52:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快救命 克拉克 - 抓紧我\N- Help us! Clark! - Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.89,0:52:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来了 来了 来了 - 救人啊 你个混蛋\N- Okay, okay, okay! - Help, you fucking asshole!
